site_name_modal.name: Site Name Modal
site_name_modal.text: This may include the name and/or location of your client if you are the installer e.g. Mr Smith, High Street

unit_telephone_number_modal.name: Unit Telephone Number Modal
unit_telephone_number_modal.text: This is the phone number of the SIM card inside your unit as it would be contacted locally (no country code required).

code_control_modal.name: Code Control Modal
code_control_modal.text: Changing these security codes will not set them on your device. These values are for existing system setups. Please ensure you are using the right codes before modifying these values.

call_sms_to_open.name: Call SMS To Open
call_sms_to_open.text: Call or send an SMS message to your intercom to open and close your gates.

hold_open_message.name: Hold Open Message
hold_open_message.text: Send an SMS message to your intercom to keep gates open.

close_message.name: Close Message
close_message.text: Send an SMS message to your intercom to close your gates.

relay_status_message.name: Relay Status Message
relay_status_message.text: Send an SMS message to view the Relay status

keypad_codes_message.name: Keypad Codes Message
keypad_codes_message.text: Send an SMS message to view Keypad Codes

stored_numbers_message.name: Stored Numbers Message
stored_numbers_message.text: Send an SMS message to view Stored numbers

signal_level_message.name: Signal Level Message
signal_level_message.text: Send an SMS message to view the signal level

programming_passcodes_modal.name: Programming Passcodes Modal
programming_passcodes_modal.text: Save and send SMS to change programming passcode to another 4 digit passcode

access_control_passcodes_modal.name: Access Control Passcodes Modal
access_control_passcodes_modal.text: Save and send SMS to change access control passcode to another 4 digit passcode. This passcode refers to the prefix used in the SMS control of the relay. A None_stored number can also call the unit and enter this code to trigger the relay.

set_apn_volte.name: Set the APN for VoLTE/4G calling
set_apn_volte.text: Set the APN for VoLTE/4G calling

set_time_for_call_to_be_aborted.name: Set time for call to be aborted
set_time_for_call_to_be_aborted.text:
Set a time for a call to be aborted if it is answered to quickly (1_9 seconds). 

        This feature is only used when the phone goes straight to voicemail or when airplane mode is switched on. 
        
        The default setting is disabled.

dtmf_latching_message.name: DTMF Latching Message
dtmf_latching_message.text:
By disabling this feature it will disable the option to latch (hold open) your gates via the keypad on your phone when a call is received. 

        This is advised if pressing 2 by mistake when trying to trigger the gate only. You can still use this feature via the SMS process. 
        
        The default setting is enabled.

call_times_message.name: Call Times Message
call_times_message.text:
Set the time for dialing each number before dialing the next (10_99 seconds) 

        The default setting is 20.

max_talk_time.name: Max Talk Time
max_talk_time.text:
"Set the maximum talk time (5 â€“ 9999 seconds) 

        The default setting is 60. "

caller_id_numbers.name: Caller ID Numbers
caller_id_numbers.text: Add up to 8 caller ID numbers at a time (maximum of 25).

keypad_code_text.name: Keypad Code Text
keypad_code_text.text:
Add up to 5 keypad codes at a time (maximum of 25) each with their own relay activation time (0_10 seconds). 

        Relay activation time is pre_set to the default time of 1 second. 
        
        Note:
        0 seconds = latch option (enter once to hold on, enter once to release).
